---
title: Fragrant Lamb Shank Korma with Mustard Seed Beans and Fluffy Rice
description: This Lamb Shank Korma with Beans & Rice is bursting full of flavours and make the perfect dinner night option, from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fragrant-lamb-shank-korma-e0c61fa9-8445462e.jpg
